WEBVTT

48:01.942 --> 48:02.817
What did you say?

48:04.442 --> 48:06.734
Understood your dad's wish...

48:09.609 --> 48:10.275
Got it.

48:10.817 --> 48:12.275
I need to go to your office at once.

48:14.775 --> 48:17.359
Check in the paper two weeks
before every victim's death.

48:17.525 --> 48:18.859
Search the November issue.

48:24.442 --> 48:26.109
He told 'I will cure our dad'.

48:26.400 --> 48:27.859
He said that's his ambition.
